      <short>
         <en><![CDATA[Enhanced software asset management with compliance checking for GLPI]]></en>
         <zh_CN><![CDATA[GLPI增强型软件资产管理与合规检查插件]]></zh_CN>
      </short>
      <long>
         <en><![CDATA[
This plugin enhances GLPI's software asset management capabilities by providing:
- Software inventory management with blacklist/whitelist functionality
- Automated compliance scanning and reporting
- Email notifications for violations
- Detailed compliance reports
- Integration with GLPI's existing software inventory

The plugin helps organizations maintain software compliance by automatically scanning installed software against configured blacklists and whitelists, generating detailed reports, and notifying administrators of violations.
         ]]></en>
         <zh_CN><![CDATA[
本插件增强了GLPI的软件资产管理能力，提供以下功能：
- 基于黑白名单的软件清单管理
- 自动化合规扫描和报告
- 违规邮件通知
- 详细的合规报告
- 与GLPI现有软件清单的集成

该插件通过自动扫描已安装软件与配置的黑白名单进行对比，生成详细报告，并通知管理员违规情况，帮助组织维护软件合规性。
         ]]></zh_CN>
      </long>
